messages.speech:
Call 105 to speak with the nursing staff if you are in Egypt or if you are in another country. Talk to the nursing staff for this country
Based on the answers you provided, please contact the nursing staff so that a member of the nursing team can evaluate the symptoms.
Please do not go to the emergency department, or visit clinics unless those symptoms worsen due to the appearance of symptoms on you. Please do a self-quarantine until the results of your analyzes become available. Self-isolation means not going to public places, staying at home and not meeting visitors.
Do not share personal items such as dishes, utensils and towels, and wash your hands occasionally.
How else may I help?
